#!/usr/bin/env python3
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
# Problem: https://yandex.ru/school/problems/kefir/
# Language: python3

n = int(input())
a = int(input())
b = int(input())
c = int(input())

if n // a >= b // c:
    print(n // a)
else:
    print(b // c + (n % a) // a)

#!/usr/bin/env python3
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
# Problem: https://yandex.ru/school/problems/kefir/
# Language: python3

n = int(input())
a = int(input())
b = int(input())
c = int(input())

if n >= b:
    print(n // b)
elif n >= a:
    print(n // a + n % b // c)
else:
    print(n // a + n % b // c - 1)
